Software
========
Below is a list of software that is required for SMPE.  The optional
software is optional (duh) but highly recommended for increased
performance.

Required
--------

  * libxml2 (http://xmlsoft.org/downloads.html)
  * libxslt (http://xmlsoft.org/downloads.html)
  * lxml >= 2.0.7 (http://codespeak.net/lxml/index.html)
  * ElementTree >= 1.3 (http://svn.effbot.org/public/elementtree-1.3/)


Optional
--------

  * cjson >= 1.0.5
  * cElementTree >= 1.0.6 (http://svn.effbot.org/public/celementtree/)

Debian Install
--------------

General:
apt-get install build-essential libssl-dev xinetd openssl sysvconfig rsync nfs-common ssh openssh-server python-flup python-imaging python-markdown python-xapian python-cjson python-psycopg2 python-docutils python-setuptools imagemagick wv libwv-dev memcached -y

Populous:
apt-get install build-essential apache2-mpm-prefork python-imaging python-markdown python-xapian python-cjson python-psycopg2 python-docutils imagemagick wv libwv-dev memcached -y

AND

Python-memcached API:
    ftp://ftp.tummy.com/pub/python-memcached/python-memcached-1.43.tar.gz